ting to deliver an unforgettable virtual reality experience.\n\nGame Features:\n\n    Immersive VR Environment:\n        Experience a meticulously crafted, enormous space brought to life with state-of-the-art VR graphics. The game environment is designed to be visually stunning and deeply immersive, making you feel like you are truly inside a high-tech, futuristic world.\n\n    Stealth and Strategy Gameplay:\n        Engage in challenging stealth gameplay that requires careful planning and quick reflexes. Utilize shadows, create diversions, and use high-tech gadgets to avoid being detected by the vigilant room owner.", "short_description": "Description:\nImmerse yourself in the thrilling world of \"Stealthy Swipers,\" a cutting-edge VR game where your mission is to \"borrow\" valuable items from a vast, high-tech environment while evading detection by the colossal room owner. This game combines intense stealth mechanics, strategic gameplay, and a rich, futuristic setting to deliver an unforgettable virtual reality experience."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/stealthyswipers/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "FQWEFWQ Invention", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/stealthyswipers", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1592192974313489"}, {"id": "1436351953220286"}, {"id": "459781504968480"}], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED_FOR_SOME_CONTENT", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_i